# Password files - never commit
.passwords
*.passwords.txt

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Temp files
*.tmp
*~

# Raw writeup files (full writeups with flags) - only in password-protected ZIPs
**/files/
**/writeup.md
**/WRITEUP.md
**/full_writeup.md

# Keep password-protected archives
!**/*_LOCKED.zip
!**/*_LOCKED.pdf
